1
00:01:30,220 --> 00:01:32,980
Episode 16

2
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,310
She said if you

3
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:39,640
don't help her son

4
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:40,310
find a job,

5
00:01:40,790 --> 00:01:42,040
she won't take Mr. He back.

6
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,350
She's clinging to you.

7
00:01:45,430 --> 00:01:46,310
I knew it.

8
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,120
He Yongwang wouldn't be such a trouble.

9
00:01:49,350 --> 00:01:50,710
He Xiaoju is really something.

10
00:01:51,430 --> 00:01:52,790
Mr. He isn't young anymore.

11
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,070
If he keeps curling up like this,

12
00:01:54,430 --> 00:01:55,840
I'm afraid it will affect his health.

13
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,150
I wonder if He Xiaoju

14
00:01:57,230 --> 00:01:58,400
takes care of his meals.

15
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,310
So many provisions?

16
00:02:49,030 --> 00:02:50,240
It seems you're well-prepared.

17
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,630
It's not like that.

18
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,240
Did He Xiaoju force you?

19
00:03:02,470 --> 00:03:03,310
We're only asking

20
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,310
for a favor.

21
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,590
This is my stall.

22
00:03:09,750 --> 00:03:10,150
You are

23
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,360
affecting my business.

24
00:03:11,710 --> 00:03:12,680
I can call the police.

25
00:03:13,910 --> 00:03:14,750
You won't

26
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:17,190
tell others who I am.

27
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,910
It'd be too embarrassing.

28
00:03:20,750 --> 00:03:21,590
If I were afraid of that,

29
00:03:21,630 --> 00:03:22,870
I wouldn't have gone back

30
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:23,910
to meet you people.

31
00:03:30,470 --> 00:03:31,430
I thought you'd be hungry,

32
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,030
so I bought you two meals,

33
00:03:33,750 --> 00:03:34,840
one Chinese and one Western.

34
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,870
But since you're well prepared,

35
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,470
I guess it's not necessary.

36
00:03:39,630 --> 00:03:40,430
As things stand,

37
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:41,000
you are

38
00:03:41,030 --> 00:03:42,240
going to sleep here tonight.

39
00:03:43,150 --> 00:03:44,400
There's a folding bed inside.

40
00:03:44,590 --> 00:03:45,750
You can just sleep on it.

41
00:03:46,030 --> 00:03:46,910
And if it rains,

42
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:47,840
there are tarps.

43
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:49,470
Don't get yourself wet.

44
00:03:50,190 --> 00:03:51,150
I won't stay with you.

45
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:52,360
Ms. Fang!

46
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,430
Business was good today.

47
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,630
I sold six pairs of jeans.

48
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:55,360
Good.

49
00:03:55,590 --> 00:03:56,520
More sales, more bonus.

50
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,400
We haven't opened for two days.

51
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,190
It's not that I'm worried
about our sales.

52
00:04:12,190 --> 00:04:13,960
I'm really worried
about Mr. He's condition.

53
00:04:14,590 --> 00:04:15,630
Maybe we should

54
00:04:15,710 --> 00:04:16,830
pay them off with some money.

55
00:04:17,750 --> 00:04:18,480
No.

56
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,800
I absolutely won't
let He Xiaoju succeed.

57
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,120
Honestly,

58
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:24,240
your sister is a real shrew.

59
00:04:24,310 --> 00:04:24,920
Does she just

60
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,240
use her old man as a tool?

61
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:27,160
The point is,

62
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,390
this won't solve anything.

63
00:04:29,430 --> 00:04:30,310
So annoying.

64
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:32,160
Let's have dinner. It's ready.

65
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,240
Someone paged.

66
00:04:35,630 --> 00:04:36,630
See who it is for me.

67
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:42,600
I think it's Mr. Gao.

68
00:04:48,270 --> 00:04:49,000
I've got an idea!

69
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:51,310
Latest international trends!

70
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:52,630
All export-level goods!

71
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,240
Buy a pair of jeans

72
00:04:54,430 --> 00:04:56,430
and get two pairs of socks!

73
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,630
Your choice

74
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:59,160
of color and style!

75
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:01,310
Come take a look!

76
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,120
Buy a pair of jeans

77
00:05:03,190 --> 00:05:05,390
and get two pairs of socks.

78
00:05:21,750 --> 00:05:22,920
Buy a pair of jeans...

79
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:23,510
Everyone, leave!

80
00:05:23,510 --> 00:05:24,240
Out of the way!

81
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,240
Move!

82
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:26,360
Step aside!

83
00:05:29,190 --> 00:05:29,950
Xiang, you came!

84
00:05:33,190 --> 00:05:33,950
Fang Wanzhi!

85
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:36,040
You can run,

86
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,560
but you can't hide.

87
00:05:38,190 --> 00:05:39,870
I've finally caught you today.

88
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:41,510
Xiang...

89
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,000
We're not that close.

90
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:44,040
Don't try to talk it out.

91
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:45,310
Pay up!

92
00:05:45,950 --> 00:05:46,360
Xiang,

93
00:05:46,430 --> 00:05:47,000
when have I

94
00:05:47,070 --> 00:05:48,070
ever failed to pay a debt?

95
00:05:48,390 --> 00:05:50,040
I'm just having some trouble right now.

96
00:05:50,190 --> 00:05:51,680
This batch of goods isn't selling well.

97
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:52,680
Your business has

98
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,750
nothing to do with me.

99
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,870
Xiang, give me a few more days.

100
00:06:01,190 --> 00:06:02,000
Cut the crap!

101
00:06:02,750 --> 00:06:04,630
Pay up, you hear me?

102
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:07,430
My boss said

103
00:06:08,310 --> 00:06:09,510
if you don't pay up today,

104
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,600
we'll mess up your face!

105
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:12,920
Oh, please don't!

106
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,390
We can work something out.

107
00:06:14,830 --> 00:06:16,430
I really don't have money.

108
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,870
But my dad does.

109
00:06:18,310 --> 00:06:18,920
Your dad does?

110
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,310
He knew I was in debt,

111
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:21,240
so he came all the way

112
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,190
to help me pay it off.

113
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,160
Where is your dad?

114
00:06:27,190 --> 00:06:28,800
There... That one...

115
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,360
He has money?

116
00:06:35,830 --> 00:06:37,040
He doesn't have it with him.

117
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,430
But he said he'd come up with it.

118
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,360
He's working on it.

119
00:06:40,070 --> 00:06:40,950
Fang Wanzhi?

120
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,430
Are you kidding me?

121
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,040
You hired such a poor old man

122
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:44,920
to play your dad?

123
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,920
You're trying to dodge your debt,

124
00:06:46,950 --> 00:06:47,480
aren't you?

125
00:06:48,510 --> 00:06:49,040
Brothers!

126
00:06:49,310 --> 00:06:50,430
Smash her stall!

127
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,390
Tear it down!

128
00:06:51,390 --> 00:06:52,190
Back off!

129
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:52,720
Xiang!

130
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:55,390
Back off!

131
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:58,160
I'm her father!

132
00:06:58,390 --> 00:06:59,600
No one touches her!

133
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,310
Or I'll fight you to the death!

134
00:07:02,950 --> 00:07:03,630
To... To the death?

135
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:05,000
Is there no law

136
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,360
in a big city like Shenzhen?

137
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,800
Paying back debts is only right!

138
00:07:10,070 --> 00:07:10,920
You're her dad?

139
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,480
Then pay up for her!

140
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,430
How much does she owe you?

141
00:07:16,430 --> 00:07:17,040
A hundred grand!

142
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,630
I didn't want you to know.

143
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:24,600
You should have left.

144
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,560
Oh, you silly girl!

145
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,240
You're quite bold!

146
00:07:28,750 --> 00:07:30,510
How did you end up owing him so much?

147
00:07:31,950 --> 00:07:32,870
I came to Shenzhen

148
00:07:32,870 --> 00:07:34,240
alone with nothing.

149
00:07:34,750 --> 00:07:36,240
How can I do business without money?

150
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,070
I have to pay rent,

151
00:07:38,070 --> 00:07:38,950
buy goods,

152
00:07:38,950 --> 00:07:40,310
and cover warehouse

153
00:07:40,630 --> 00:07:41,630
and staff costs.

154
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:44,510
Have you ever

155
00:07:44,510 --> 00:07:45,750
raised me, even for a single day?

156
00:07:46,390 --> 00:07:47,240
Since you're here,

157
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,190
pay the money for me.

158
00:07:48,190 --> 00:07:49,270
Then we'll be even.

159
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,720
Hey, gentlemen!

160
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:58,800
Put the knife down first!

161
00:07:59,070 --> 00:08:01,120
Please, I'm begging you.

162
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,270
I... I'm her father.

163
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,560
I know my daughter.

164
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,360
She's strong-willed.

165
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,510
She'll definitely

166
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,750
repay the money.

167
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:11,240
Just let her off today for my sake,

168
00:08:11,270 --> 00:08:11,870
please?

169
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:14,510
Dad?

170
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,560
What are you doing?

171
00:08:17,070 --> 00:08:17,870
Debt collectors.

172
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:21,000
She owes them 100,000 yuan.

173
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,070
That much?

174
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:24,160
You think you're worth that?

175
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:25,160
Let's just go!

176
00:08:25,310 --> 00:08:26,480
It's none of our business!

177
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,430
My bag...

178
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,240
It has nothing to do with you! Go!

179
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,160
Wait...

180
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:32,790
Let's go!

181
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,510
Come on! Hurry!

182
00:08:35,030 --> 00:08:35,910
Let's get out of here.

183
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:37,910
Hey!

184
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,630
Why are you leaving already?

185
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,270
Who's going to pay then?

186
00:08:48,270 --> 00:08:48,910
Students,

187
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,480
that concludes our social practice.

188
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:51,630
You all saw that?

189
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:52,670
It's so hard

190
00:08:52,790 --> 00:08:53,550
for one to start

191
00:08:53,550 --> 00:08:54,600
a business in Shenzhen.

192
00:08:54,910 --> 00:08:55,720
But this is not

193
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:56,790
a common occurrence.

194
00:08:56,910 --> 00:08:58,000
No need to write a report.

195
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:58,910
You can go back now.

196
00:08:59,030 --> 00:08:59,960
Okay.

197
00:09:14,870 --> 00:09:15,720
He's really your dad?

198
00:09:16,630 --> 00:09:17,670
Biologically, yes.

199
00:09:19,870 --> 00:09:21,030
And that woman is my sister.

200
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:22,910
Also biologically.

201
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,550
He seemed pretty nice.

202
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:30,080
I almost couldn't keep up the act.

203
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:34,670
Thanks.

204
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,080
The money.

205
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,550
It's 130,000 yuan in total.

206
00:09:44,790 --> 00:09:45,960
I already paid back 30,000,

207
00:09:46,270 --> 00:09:47,150
so I still owe 100,000.

208
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,550
I'll repay the principal today,

209
00:09:50,790 --> 00:09:52,200
and cover the interest next month

210
00:09:52,390 --> 00:09:53,390
at the yearly rate.

211
00:09:53,870 --> 00:09:54,390
No need.

212
00:09:54,670 --> 00:09:56,120
And don't rush to pay the principal.

213
00:09:56,750 --> 00:09:57,150
You should

214
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,150
settle things with

215
00:09:58,150 --> 00:09:58,870
your dad first.

216
00:10:03,030 --> 00:10:04,720
Money can't solve this.

217
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:06,870
Tell your four students

218
00:10:06,910 --> 00:10:08,200
who lent me the money

219
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,480
that I'm truly grateful.

220
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,480
I'll treat them to drinks

221
00:10:12,550 --> 00:10:13,750
when I repay the interest.

222
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,510
I can't let you carry favors for me.

223
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:18,790
Your dad's right.

224
00:10:19,790 --> 00:10:21,150
You really are strong-willed.

225
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,200
He's not my dad.

226
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:24,000
You just said it.

227
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,630
He's only my biological father,

228
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,030
not the one I recognize in my heart.

229
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,670
But he was ready to fight us

230
00:10:29,750 --> 00:10:30,910
to the death for you.

231
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,200
No need to remind me!

232
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,120
I'm not blind!

233
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:33,790
Wanzhi!

234
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,670
What's wrong with you?

235
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,790
Mr. Gao is here to help.

236
00:10:37,870 --> 00:10:38,870
Why are you upset?

237
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:40,670
It's not her fault.

238
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:41,840
Don't blame her.

239
00:10:42,550 --> 00:10:43,270
I'll take it, then.

240
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,200
Call me if you need anything.

241
00:11:17,550 --> 00:11:18,960
I've completely cut ties

242
00:11:20,790 --> 00:11:21,670
with Shenxian Peak.

243
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,080
No one will come to me

244
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,360
except for Yang Hui now.

245
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,000
And what about

246
00:11:31,030 --> 00:11:32,000
that niece of yours?

247
00:11:32,750 --> 00:11:33,750
Even her mom doesn't care.

248
00:11:33,790 --> 00:11:34,910
Why should I?

249
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:37,320
I'll act like I never met her.

250
00:11:52,510 --> 00:11:53,390
Fang?

251
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:02,550
Ms. Fang is really cultured,

252
00:12:03,270 --> 00:12:04,720
giving you such a nice name.

253
00:12:04,910 --> 00:12:05,750
I don't even know

254
00:12:05,790 --> 00:12:07,510
how to address you.

255
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,240
How did you find this place?

256
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,390
I just followed you.

257
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:12,870
You followed me when I was closing

258
00:12:12,870 --> 00:12:13,670
my stall last night?

259
00:12:13,790 --> 00:12:14,320
Yes.

260
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:15,600
Then...

261
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,080
Where do you live?

262
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:17,870
Nowhere.

263
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,200
Your sister found

264
00:12:19,390 --> 00:12:20,550
a hotel for 10 yuan a night.

265
00:12:20,790 --> 00:12:21,600
It's too expensive.

266
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:23,960
And I stayed here

267
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:25,320
at your place all night.

268
00:12:25,670 --> 00:12:26,120
What...

269
00:12:30,670 --> 00:12:32,000
You're still not giving up?

270
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:33,390
No.

271
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,270
I'm just worried.

272
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:37,630
I've sent you to a good family.

273
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,670
But how did you end up like this,

274
00:12:40,030 --> 00:12:41,630
owing so much money?

275
00:12:44,510 --> 00:12:46,150
After my mom died, I got into trouble.

276
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,390
I was extorted

277
00:12:47,390 --> 00:12:48,510
for tens of thousands of yuan

278
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,910
and fell out with Vice Mayor Meng.

279
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:53,080
So I came to Shenzhen alone.

280
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:56,080
Then you should just work hard

281
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:57,670
and live steadily.

282
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,030
Running such a big business

283
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:00,320
without capital?

284
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,510
This is too risky.

285
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:03,200
It's none of your concern.

286
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:04,870
It's not.

287
00:13:05,670 --> 00:13:06,790
You're right.

288
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:07,960
But I mean,

289
00:13:08,510 --> 00:13:09,960
you can still go back.

290
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,240
You still have

291
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:12,870
a home in Yu County.

292
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:14,630
Your family has a nice house.

293
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:15,600
I've been there.

294
00:13:17,150 --> 00:13:18,670
You can ask Vice Mayor Meng

295
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:20,150
to help you

296
00:13:20,670 --> 00:13:21,960
