This is for you.

887
00:34:14,630 --> 00:34:15,840
Your dividend

888
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:16,960
for seven point five shares,

889
00:34:17,150 --> 00:34:18,000
plus back pay

890
00:34:18,030 --> 00:34:19,280
and overtime for the year.

891
00:34:19,800 --> 00:34:20,670
After deducting 8,000,

892
00:34:21,230 --> 00:34:22,150
this is what's left.

893
00:34:22,590 --> 00:34:23,400
That's too much!

894
00:34:23,480 --> 00:34:24,440
And why pay me overtime?

895
00:34:24,590 --> 00:34:25,400
It's not much.

896
00:34:25,590 --> 00:34:27,110
Your shares were already small.

897
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:28,630
I've also booked you

898
00:34:28,710 --> 00:34:30,480
a sleeper train ticket for tomorrow.

899
00:34:33,590 --> 00:34:34,000
Also...

900
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:35,000
There's more?

901
00:34:35,280 --> 00:34:36,190
I went to Zhongying Street

902
00:34:36,230 --> 00:34:37,630
and bought you some local specialties.

903
00:34:37,960 --> 00:34:38,880
Both for your mom

904
00:34:39,030 --> 00:34:40,000
and your mother-in-law.

905
00:34:40,320 --> 00:34:40,920
New Year gifts.

906
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:44,230
Why are you so considerate?

907
00:34:45,230 --> 00:34:45,760
Wait a second.

908
00:34:46,150 --> 00:34:47,070
I've also got you a gift.

909
00:34:50,550 --> 00:34:51,000
Look!

910
00:34:51,110 --> 00:34:51,960
What is this?

911
00:34:54,710 --> 00:34:55,360
A mobile phone?

912
00:34:55,440 --> 00:34:56,000
Yeah.

913
00:34:56,150 --> 00:34:57,360
Pagers are out of trend now.

914
00:34:57,510 --> 00:34:58,550
This suits you more.

915
00:35:00,710 --> 00:35:01,320
Juan,

916
00:35:02,110 --> 00:35:04,150
you asked me for an advance
to buy a mobile phone

917
00:35:04,840 --> 00:35:05,590
for me?

918
00:35:10,110 --> 00:35:10,670
This won't do.

919
00:35:11,280 --> 00:35:12,880
What's wrong?

920
00:35:13,150 --> 00:35:14,480
You're a businesswoman now.

921
00:35:14,550 --> 00:35:15,070
You'll be

922
00:35:15,070 --> 00:35:16,190
discussing big deals.

923
00:35:16,400 --> 00:35:17,030
You need this.

924
00:35:17,150 --> 00:35:18,400
Who should I call?

925
00:35:19,510 --> 00:35:19,880
Right.

926
00:35:20,070 --> 00:35:20,760
You.

927
00:35:21,000 --> 00:35:21,840
I'll buy you one too.

928
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:22,710
I don't need it.

929
00:35:23,070 --> 00:35:24,280
I'm not good at negotiations.

930
00:35:24,960 --> 00:35:25,670
Then take some money.

931
00:35:26,630 --> 00:35:28,070
You look down on me?

932
00:35:28,630 --> 00:35:29,230
No...

933
00:35:29,230 --> 00:35:30,110
Alright!

934
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:33,320
I'm so happy

935
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:34,030
to see you

936
00:35:34,070 --> 00:35:35,670
overcome such a huge hurdle

937
00:35:36,360 --> 00:35:37,360
this year.

938
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:38,840
If you still value me,

939
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:40,000
just take the phone.

940
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:41,230
This is a memento of us

941
00:35:41,320 --> 00:35:43,360
venturing into Shenzhen together.

942
00:35:43,840 --> 00:35:45,360
But you also need a memento.

943
00:35:45,590 --> 00:35:46,630
I must buy you something.

944
00:35:47,070 --> 00:35:47,710
How about this?

945
00:35:48,320 --> 00:35:49,150
After New Year,

946
00:35:49,230 --> 00:35:50,230
buy me a pager with

947
00:35:50,360 --> 00:35:51,110
a Chinese display.

948
00:35:51,150 --> 00:35:52,630
I really don't need a phone.

949
00:35:57,440 --> 00:35:58,920
I don't need to take a cab.

950
00:35:59,550 --> 00:36:00,360
You have to.

951
00:36:01,320 --> 00:36:02,760
If you hadn't booked me the ticket,

952
00:36:03,230 --> 00:36:04,710
I'd probably have stayed until tomorrow.

953
00:36:05,320 --> 00:36:05,960
Why?

954
00:36:06,440 --> 00:36:07,800
It's Little New Year today.

955
00:36:08,480 --> 00:36:09,150
I was thinking of

956
00:36:09,280 --> 00:36:10,320
making you some dumplings.

957
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:12,550
You know what?

958
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:14,000
I haven't had dumplings for long.

959
00:36:14,630 --> 00:36:15,920
Come with me for
the next New Year.

960
00:36:16,360 --> 00:36:17,710
I'll make you dumplings

961
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:18,710
the whole holiday,

962
00:36:18,920 --> 00:36:20,030
with all kinds of fillings.

963
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:21,630
I'll cook five at a time,

964
00:36:21,840 --> 00:36:23,510
making sure every bite is hot.

965
00:36:25,710 --> 00:36:27,510
You're making my mouth water.

966
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:32,480
Sir, please open the boot.

967
00:36:38,400 --> 00:36:39,000
I'll pick you up

968
00:36:39,230 --> 00:36:40,440
on the same date as before.

969
00:36:40,670 --> 00:36:41,510
If there are any changes,

970
00:36:41,670 --> 00:36:42,360
just call me.

971
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:43,630
I'm someone

972
00:36:43,710 --> 00:36:45,230
with a mobile phone now.

973
00:36:46,550 --> 00:36:47,230
I'll be back soon!

974
00:37:37,070 --> 00:37:38,150
You've got a phone now?

975
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:41,550
Do you know how to save numbers?

976
00:37:42,190 --> 00:37:43,550
Save my number first.

977
00:37:44,030 --> 00:37:46,000
We can stay in touch more conveniently.

978
00:37:47,550 --> 00:37:48,710
Treat me to dumplings?

979
00:37:49,150 --> 00:37:49,920
Okay!

980
00:37:50,590 --> 00:37:52,030
I know a dumpling restaurant.

981
00:37:52,070 --> 00:37:52,710
Very authentic.

982
00:37:53,150 --> 00:37:53,880
Put the address down.

983
00:37:55,590 --> 00:37:56,960
Here, have some tea.

984
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:57,800
Thanks.

985
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:58,480
Ready to order?

986
00:38:00,550 --> 00:38:01,320
Dumplings.

987
00:38:01,550 --> 00:38:03,030
Pickled cabbage dumplings, okay?

988
00:38:03,190 --> 00:38:03,590
Okay.

989
00:38:03,840 --> 00:38:04,360
Our signature.

990
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:06,550
Shrimp and corn dumplings, too.

991
00:38:07,110 --> 00:38:08,110
Shrimp and corn.

992
00:38:20,110 --> 00:38:21,000
Here, some more water.

993
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:23,480
Thanks.

994
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:28,150
Why isn't he here yet?

995
00:38:31,480 --> 00:38:32,230
Are you hungry?

996
00:38:32,670 --> 00:38:33,880
How about I cook you some first?

997
00:38:40,190 --> 00:38:41,000
I'll wait a bit longer.

998
00:38:43,030 --> 00:38:43,550
Fine.

999
00:38:54,550 --> 00:38:54,920
Here,

1000
00:38:55,880 --> 00:38:57,030
have some dumpling soup first.

1001
00:38:58,320 --> 00:38:59,070
Thank you.

1002
00:39:01,400 --> 00:39:03,190
Is he coming or not?

1003
00:39:03,670 --> 00:39:05,510
I'm going back to my hometown
for the New Year.

1004
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:06,670
I might miss

1005
00:39:06,840 --> 00:39:08,630
the train if he doesn't come soon.

1006
00:39:12,800 --> 00:39:13,510
I'll go elsewhere.

1007
00:39:14,030 --> 00:39:14,510
Then...

1008
00:39:15,360 --> 00:39:16,320
Sorry! So sorry!

1009
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:18,230
I'm late.

1010
00:39:19,190 --> 00:39:20,280
You're late?

1011
00:39:20,670 --> 00:39:21,800
I waited for you for two hours!

1012
00:39:21,960 --> 00:39:22,760
This is outrageous!

1013
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:24,630
I'm so sorry.

1014
00:39:24,880 --> 00:39:25,760
You didn't answer my calls.

1015
00:39:27,630 --> 00:39:28,360
I'm really sorry.

1016
00:39:28,880 --> 00:39:30,110
I was afraid you'd scold me.

1017
00:39:30,510 --> 00:39:32,360
So you did it on purpose?

1018
00:39:32,550 --> 00:39:33,360
Oh! Don't hit him!

1019
00:39:33,710 --> 00:39:34,360
It's my fault.

1020
00:39:34,550 --> 00:39:35,590
If I hadn't said anything,

1021
00:39:35,760 --> 00:39:36,880
she wouldn't have gotten angry.

1022
00:39:37,110 --> 00:39:38,190
Today's Little New Year.

1023
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:39,510
It's so nice for you two to eat

1024
00:39:39,590 --> 00:39:40,400
dumplings together!

1025
00:39:40,510 --> 00:39:41,150
Don't argue!

1026
00:39:41,190 --> 00:39:41,800
We are not...

1027
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:42,550
Just come at me.

1028
00:39:42,800 --> 00:39:43,480
Come at me.

1029
00:39:43,590 --> 00:39:44,550
She only means well.

1030
00:39:44,880 --> 00:39:45,630
Have you ordered yet?

1031
00:39:45,800 --> 00:39:46,440
- Go cook!
- She has!

1032
00:39:46,480 --> 00:39:47,320
Alright, I'll go cook.

1033
00:39:47,510 --> 00:39:49,000
She's in a hurry to leave!

1034
00:39:49,480 --> 00:39:50,280
You're so late.

1035
00:39:50,320 --> 00:39:51,670
She still has a train to catch.

1036
00:39:52,150 --> 00:39:52,670
Oh, ma'am,

1037
00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:53,440
don't cook.

1038
00:39:54,480 --> 00:39:55,480
They are already wrapped.

1039
00:39:55,550 --> 00:39:56,360
If I freeze them now,

1040
00:39:56,400 --> 00:39:57,480
I can't sell them anymore.

1041
00:39:58,510 --> 00:39:59,110
Fine, cook them!

1042
00:39:59,400 --> 00:39:59,880
Go ahead.

1043
00:40:00,070 --> 00:40:00,670
After it's done,

1044
00:40:00,710 --> 00:40:02,070
you'd better eat them fast.

1045
00:40:02,550 --> 00:40:03,880
I told your wife just now.

1046
00:40:04,070 --> 00:40:05,000
I need to catch a train.

1047
00:40:05,150 --> 00:40:05,960
Then pack them up.

1048
00:40:06,590 --> 00:40:07,320
Give me a few more

1049
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:08,280
bags of your seasonings.

1050
00:40:08,670 --> 00:40:09,150
Alright!

1051
00:40:09,440 --> 00:40:10,550
Coming right up!

1052
00:40:11,230 --> 00:40:11,880
I was late because

1053
00:40:11,880 --> 00:40:12,960
I took the students to

1054
00:40:12,960 --> 00:40:14,000
the station for the holiday.

1055
00:40:14,480 --> 00:40:15,150
I'm sorry.

1056
00:40:15,360 --> 00:40:16,590
Alright, come over.

1057
00:40:19,230 --> 00:40:19,920
Here, sit down.

1058
00:40:22,710 --> 00:40:23,800
Alright! Let's eat.

1059
00:40:24,590 --> 00:40:25,920
How can we eat them now?

1060
00:40:26,030 --> 00:40:27,030
They're all cold.

1061
00:40:27,320 --> 00:40:28,230
Li Juan said

1062
00:40:28,230 --> 00:40:30,110
dumplings should be eaten
while they are hot.

1063
00:40:30,920 --> 00:40:32,190
There are ways to eat it hot

1064
00:40:32,320 --> 00:40:33,440
and also to eat it cold.

1065
00:40:33,670 --> 00:40:34,320
You see?

1066
00:40:34,670 --> 00:40:36,800
I deliberately packed extra seasonings.

1067
00:40:37,150 --> 00:40:38,590
Don't mix them up.

1068
00:40:38,920 --> 00:40:39,710
Pick up a dumpling,

1069
00:40:39,710 --> 00:40:41,510
dip it in each of the seasonings,
and taste it.

1070
00:40:41,710 --> 00:40:42,800
This way of eating is called...

1071
00:40:42,840 --> 00:40:44,000
Dumpling sashimi.

1072
00:40:44,280 --> 00:40:45,150
Never heard of it.

1073
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:47,280
There are many you haven't heard of.

1074
00:40:47,550 --> 00:40:48,280
Give it a try.

1075
00:40:48,590 --> 00:40:49,800
The joy of life lies in

1076
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:50,920
constantly trying new things.

1077
00:40:51,510 --> 00:40:52,800
If you hadn't helped me in that

1078
00:40:52,840 --> 00:40:53,440
critical moment,

1079
00:40:53,590 --> 00:40:54,960
I'd have fallen out with you today.

1080
00:40:59,360 --> 00:41:00,360
Happy New Year.

1081
00:41:02,030 --> 00:41:03,000
It's too soon to say that.

1082
00:41:03,150 --> 00:41:04,070
Still several days left.

1083
00:41:04,760 --> 00:41:06,320
Don't you know it's Little New Year?

1084
00:41:07,190 --> 00:41:07,880
Little New Year?

1085
00:41:07,920 --> 00:41:10,000
Isn't it the day before New Year's Eve?

1086
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:12,190
Today's only the 23rd day
of the last lunar month.

1087
00:41:13,030 --> 00:41:13,440
But...

1088
00:41:14,510 --> 00:41:15,030
I see.

1089
00:41:15,320 --> 00:41:16,440
Customs vary from place to place.

1090
00:41:17,030 --> 00:41:17,550
Yes.

1091
00:41:17,760 --> 00:41:18,590
I heard some celebrate

1092
00:41:18,630 --> 00:41:19,400
Little New Year

1093
00:41:19,440 --> 00:41:20,230
on the 24th day.

1094
00:41:21,070 --> 00:41:21,880
We are in Shenzhen,

1095
00:41:22,230 --> 00:41:23,190
where people come from

1096
00:41:23,190 --> 00:41:24,150
all over the country.

1097
00:41:24,550 --> 00:41:25,550
It's inclusive here. Cheers!

1098
00:41:25,710 --> 00:41:26,920
Happy Little New Year!

1099
00:41:37,550 --> 00:41:38,070
What's this?

1100
00:41:38,590 --> 00:41:39,440
Interest.

1101
00:41:41,000 --> 00:41:41,360
Right.

1102
00:41:41,590 --> 00:41:42,480
Time to settle it.

1103
00:41:42,880 --> 00:41:44,360
I promised to settle it
before the New Year.

1104
00:41:44,710 --> 00:41:45,760
Give me time to calculate.

1105
00:41:46,030 --> 00:41:46,760
No need.

1106
00:41:46,760 --> 00:41:47,590
I've done the math.

1107
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:49,880
Interest is calculated at eight percent.

1108
00:41:50,880 --> 00:41:52,000
That's not right!

1109
00:41:52,920 --> 00:41:54,110
You didn't read the contracts,

1110
00:41:54,110 --> 00:41:54,710
did you?

1111
00:41:55,190 --> 00:41:56,030
I negotiated

1112
00:41:56,030 --> 00:41:57,070
those contracts separately.

1113
00:41:57,150 --> 00:41:58,030
Even the highest

1114
00:41:58,070 --> 00:41:59,510
interest rate wasn't eight percent.

1115
00:41:59,840 --> 00:42:00,400
Some are

1116
00:42:00,480 --> 00:42:02,280
settled monthly for terms
under three months,

1117
00:42:02,320 --> 00:42:03,440
while others are calculated

1118
00:42:03,510 --> 00:42:05,030
annually for terms over three months.

1119
00:42:05,480 --> 00:42:05,840
Oh, and

1120
00:42:06,070 --> 00:42:07,070
didn't you repay

1121
00:42:07,110 --> 00:42:08,190
30,000 yuan in advance?

1122
00:42:08,550 --> 00:42:09,920
He said no interest would be charged.

1123
00:42:15,070 --> 00:42:16,030
When you borrowed money,

1124
00:42:16,030 --> 00:42:17,000
did you ever think about

1125
00:42:17,320 --> 00:42:18,000
what would happen

1126
00:42:18,110 --> 00:42:19,150
if I couldn't pay it back?

1127
00:42:20,150 --> 00:42:20,710
I did.

1128
00:42:21,400 --> 00:42:22,440
Then, as the guarantor,

1129
00:42:22,480 --> 00:42:23,480
I'd be responsible.

1130
00:42:24,190 --> 00:42:25,760
You've calculated everything so clearly.

1131
00:42:26,190 --> 00:42:27,150
You, the guarantor,

1132
00:42:27,190 --> 00:42:28,280
won't make any money.

1133
00:42:29,760 --> 00:42:31,400
I didn't put any money in.
Why make money?

1134
00:42:32,230 --> 00:42:33,960
Besides, we're friends.

1135
00:42:34,150 --> 00:42:35,150
It's only right to help.

1136
00:42:35,400 --> 00:42:36,070
See, you even

1137
00:42:36,110 --> 00:42:37,360
treated me to dumplings.

1138
00:42:37,800 --> 00:42:39,110
Those who put in money

1139
00:42:39,190 --> 00:42:40,150
also earn interest,

1140
00:42:40,480 --> 00:42:41,360
higher than from a bank.

1141
00:42:41,400 --> 00:42:42,510
They'll thank me for that.

1142
00:42:42,800 --> 00:42:44,190
I gained favors from both sides,

1143
00:42:44,320 --> 00:42:45,360
so why not?

1144
00:42:47,320 --> 00:42:48,070
You interrupted me.

1145
00:42:48,150 --> 00:42:49,590
I forgot the numbers now.

1146
00:42:52,110 --> 00:42:52,710
I'll start over.
